                                    ToolTip="SWFOC_SpawnUnit → spawn the SelectedTypeId for the given Slot at (PosX, PosY, PosZ), Count copies. Slot must be &gt;= 0; Count &gt;= 1; PosZ usually 0 for ground. PHASE 2 PENDING — replay mirror only."/>
                            <TextBlock Text="{Binding Spawn.Badge}"
