                        <!-- iter 119 (2026-04-29): LIVE alternative via the iter 109 SWFOC_SpawnUnitLua wire.
                             Three Lua expressions instead of slot+typeid+pos floats. The engine call composes
                             (player):Spawn_Unit(type, position) on the engine side, so this is the
                             genuinely-LIVE counterpart to the PHASE 2 PENDING SWFOC_SpawnUnit Phase-1-mirror. -->
                        <!-- 2026-05-07 (iter 379): UX polish — header was stale at "(iter 119 LIVE)";
                             section grew through iter-195 spawn-variant batch (3 buttons: Reinforce /
                             SpawnFromPool / CreateGenericObject) on top of iter-119's single Spawn (Lua, LIVE).
                             4 LIVE wires total spanning iter 109/185. -->
