                            </StackPanel>
                        </GroupBox>
                        <!--
                            2026-05-05 (iter 203): Discovery helpers GroupBox.
                            iter-177 trio (1-arg getters) + iter-186 Find_Nearest
                            (3-arg getter). Each returns an engine handle the
                            operator can read in the status row at the bottom of
                            the tab and paste into spawn fields above. Distinct
