                                2026-04-27 (iter 35): PHASE 2 PENDING badge.
                                Per BridgeGalacticDispatcher.cs:13-15, these
                                planet owner mutation calls are Phase-2
                                pending. SWFOC_RevealAll and SWFOC_SetDiplomacy
                                are live-backed.
