                    <!--
                        2026-04-27 (iter 34) — Overlay Feature 2 surfaced.
                        Spawn a unit at a galactic-mode planet via the
                        engine's "fleet arrival" / story-event entry point
                        so the unit integrates cleanly into galactic state
                        (the editor has been able to call SWFOC_SpawnUnit
